actions.text: Referred to House Committee on Agriculture.

official_title: Resolution expressing the sense of the House of Representatives concerning an assessment by the Secretary of Agriculture of our whey supply situation.

summary.text: Expresses the sense of the House of Representatives that the Secretary of Agriculture should assess the whey supply situation and advise the House Committee on Agriculture of his findings. Directs the Department of Agriculture to begin a research program to utilize whey more efficiently.

titles.title: Resolution expressing the sense of the House of Representatives concerning an assessment by the Secretary of Agriculture of our whey supply situation.
